author: Paul Cullen
title: Italy, Austria and UK account for most imported cases of Covid-19
description: HSE report shows young people, while far less likely to get virus, have been hospitalised
content:
Italy, Austria and the UK account for most of the cases of coronavirus that were imported into Ireland, according to a new analysis of cases.
